Paper: hep-th/0207130

Date: 2002-07-12

Title: The Pre-Big Bang Scenario in String Cosmology

Authors: M. Gasperini and G. Veneziano

Comments: 250 pages, latex, 34 figures included using epsfig

Journal-ref: Phys.Rept. 373 (2003) 1-212

We review physical motivations, phenomenological consequences, and openproblems of the so-called pre-big bang scenario in superstring cosmology.